# Implement Automated Testing and Linting (Stage 2)

We will add automated code quality checks to the GitHub Actions pipeline to ensure only valid, bug-free code is released.

## Proposed Changes

### [CI/CD Configuration]

#### [MODIFY] [.github/workflows/deploy.yml](file:///c:/Users/HP/Desktop/SEO%20optimization/.github/workflows/deploy.yml)
*   Add a `lint-and-test` job that runs before `build-and-push`.
*   Include steps for:
    *   Python environment setup.
    *   `ruff` linting.
    *   `pytest` unit tests.

